勇武&hellip;&hellip;」「全民勇武？日日見你係啲po度叫人打狗殺狗，但係有行動就唔見你岀手，全民勇武唔包你自己？」老鳳便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「提倡全民勇武，不算是推人去死&hellip;&hellip;只係我無資格帶頭，無話過唔喺後面玩狙&hellip;&hellip;抗爭者的事，能算是推人去死麼」接連便是難懂的話，甚麼「有我係度隻狗死硬」，甚麼「捷克嘅係scorpion非常好用嘅槍」之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來，連登内外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"275c2c7a3b57ef366e078311397808c7200fe0fc","tid":1952314,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"又人群眾集？咁咪永續14日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c3d087d2747e505a9f74169510cc2715febe37","tid":1952314,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"有冇記者問下福壽園嗰啲有有盈喜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e20b6ce1e90029e5f60eb171b46b830e85c74f","tid":1952314,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfN5bUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfN5bUi.jpg&h=2b54b0c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"495433f9c89fd8b7bd33b8f8eddbe69bdd391a16","tid":1952314,"uid":146642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"老鳳成日叫人去打狗殺狗 唔好比老鳳呃<br />\n<br />\n聽我講句 唔好被憤怒沖昏頭腦 <br />\n<br />\n當你踏足社會 眼界廣闊就唔同想法。<br />\n<br />\n上連登勿認真 講真後生仔 讀到大學 自己識衡量下風險<br />\n<br />\n有咩得著 冒險畀人拉 諗下自己將來啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋老鳳永遠縮係背後得把口<br />\n<br />\n 推人去死 監就人地坐 自己就繼續打份政府工安安穩穩"},{"pid":"4f84bb55a8b0d5752cf6c39845a63a326ac23ccd","tid":1952314,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bad60d8b5f9abd6df074bdef6c4f946519fde817","tid":1952314,"uid":189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"80a11e70f7db460f49eb082b366b9e404af7ad63","tid":1952314,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20